### Low Level API: ChatModel
GET http://localhost:8082/model?message=What is the capital of Germany?

### High Level API: AI Service with tools
GET http://localhost:8082/assistant?message=What is the current time?
X-Session-Id: local-test-session-001
X-User-Id: local-test-user-001

### Assistant history
GET http://localhost:8082/assistant/history
X-Session-Id: local-test-session-001
X-User-Id: local-test-user-001

### Delete session
DELETE http://localhost:8082/assistant/session
X-Session-Id: local-test-session-001
X-User-Id: local-test-user-001

### Debug active sessions
GET http://localhost:8082/assistant/debug/sessions
